metadata.description:
1.61803 is a work where the feeling of tranquility and emotional stability predominates, where lighting and shadows embrace each other to create an aura that satisfies vision and serenity while looking for the details of the image. Every line and silhouette is exposed to leave the viewer thoughtful and inspired by the tasks of their daily work. Keeping an edition or having it physically in our home and observing it at the beginning of tomorrow will help you start the day on the right foot.

1.61803 is considered the most beautiful number in the universe, the golden number, the number of god according to old studies of science.
